<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/b96ea5cc4d2b4f40b1a8b4dbef149a91.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（人文楼）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>住宿齐备</strong></p>
